| Go | `parseGo()` | ~95 lines | âœ… Good â€” handles receivers, import blocks |
| Rust | `parseRust()` | ~110 lines | âœ… Good â€” handles traits, impl blocks, use statements |
| Java | `parseJava()` | ~70 lines | âœ… Adequate â€” handles classes, methods, imports |

